content.html: Today 'LIbs of Tik Tok' gained 150,000 followers, started a Substack with a $50 subscription fee, began receiving a salary by the Babylon Bee to continue tweeting, and once again went on America's most-watched news show. And this shows how CANCEL CULTURE has gone WAY too far!!!!
